  "detailed_description": "Leap, stick, and swing your way through the enchanting realms of <strong>Tongue Tale</strong> – a vibrant 2D platformer where you step into the webbed feet of a fearless blue frog!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/4323b749f9deb78d4b65ac8ebfcfa6c0.webp?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=40 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sticky Mechanics</h2>Master the art of the tongue! Use it not just to snack flies, but also to cling to walls, swing over gaping chasms, and outplay your foes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vast Worlds Awaiting</h2>Journey through 7 beautifully hand-crafted worlds, each bursting with unique challenges, secrets, and charming aesthetics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/f8c4ee2a1883f9ca395ee4f0212893ce.poster.avif?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/f8c4ee2a1883f9ca395ee4f0212893ce.webm?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/f8c4ee2a1883f9ca395ee4f0212893ce.mp4?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss Battles</h2>Confront and defeat 7 unforgettable bosses, each guarding their domain with unique skills and strategies. Test your wits and reflexes against these formidable foes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dark World</h2> If you are looking for an extra challenge, play Dark World and climb the leaderboards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/cf5e70839081823e44c51c8226bfcf53.webp?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=40 /></span><br>Battle your friends and use all the movement techniques your tongue offers to you to outplay them.<br>Beat them in 80+ Minigames to get the crown!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/a6af36d07a5e104649e000cc51979866.poster.avif?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/a6af36d07a5e104649e000cc51979866.webm?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/a6af36d07a5e104649e000cc51979866.mp4?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you navigate the challenging terrains, overcome the daunting bosses, and prove that even a tiny frog can rise to hero status? Get ready for <strong>Tongue Tale!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "Leap, stick, and swing your way through the enchanting realms of <strong>Tongue Tale</strong> – a vibrant 2D platformer where you step into the webbed feet of a fearless blue frog!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/4323b749f9deb78d4b65ac8ebfcfa6c0.webp?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=40 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sticky Mechanics</h2>Master the art of the tongue! Use it not just to snack flies, but also to cling to walls, swing over gaping chasms, and outplay your foes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vast Worlds Awaiting</h2>Journey through 7 beautifully hand-crafted worlds, each bursting with unique challenges, secrets, and charming aesthetics.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/f8c4ee2a1883f9ca395ee4f0212893ce.poster.avif?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/f8c4ee2a1883f9ca395ee4f0212893ce.webm?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/f8c4ee2a1883f9ca395ee4f0212893ce.mp4?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boss Battles</h2>Confront and defeat 7 unforgettable bosses, each guarding their domain with unique skills and strategies. Test your wits and reflexes against these formidable foes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dark World</h2> If you are looking for an extra challenge, play Dark World and climb the leaderboards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/cf5e70839081823e44c51c8226bfcf53.webp?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=40 /></span><br>Battle your friends and use all the movement techniques your tongue offers to you to outplay them.<br>Beat them in 80+ Minigames to get the crown!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/a6af36d07a5e104649e000cc51979866.poster.avif?t=1712925915\" width=618 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/a6af36d07a5e104649e000cc51979866.webm?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2573490/extras/a6af36d07a5e104649e000cc51979866.mp4?t=1712925915\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Can you navigate the challenging terrains, overcome the daunting bosses, and prove that even a tiny frog can rise to hero status? Get ready for <strong>Tongue Tale!</strong>",
